snippet.title: Rave Heart - Trailer
snippet.description:
Rave Heart's development has finally been completed! The game shall be released on steam soon. Until then, I hope you all will enjoy this trailer I put together for the game's completion. Thank you so much and I hope you all enjoy! :D

I wish to thank God first and foremost for giving me the strength to carry on in developing the game, and I wish to thank everyone who has supported me along the way in its' completion! Each and every one of you has truly helped tremendously! :)

Rave Heart on Aldorlea:
https://www.aldorlea.org/raveheart.php

Rave Heart on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1375880/Rave_Heart/

More info on Rave Heart:
https://starmage.itch.io/rave-heart
https://rpgmaker.net/games/10335/

Music:
Bitter Sweet Entertainment, Inc.
